<h1>Band 5 nurse recruitment</h1>

<p>We know that you value working in an area you enjoy&#8212;in a position that fits your career plans&#8212;so we&#8217;ve made our recruitment process easy to understand and use so you can start the job you have always dreamt of. We also have a dedicated nursing recruitment team to support you through every stage of the process</p>

<p>These positions are not open to newly qualified nurses who are recruited to our &#8216;Preceptorship programme&#8217; training scheme through dedicated campaigns.</p>
</div><!-- content -->
</div><!-- main -->

<div class="complementary">
<p class="secondary">The Trust manages all Band 5 nurse recruitment centrally and holds a number of recruitment campaigns and open days/job fairs every year. Vacancies are divided into four staff groups: General, Theatre, Critical Care and Children&#8217;s,across all our sites.</p>
</div><!-- complementary -->
</div><!-- container -->



