<h2>2015 recruitment campaigns</h2>

<p>We&#8217;ll be recruiting across a wide range of clinical practice areas at the Trust in 2015.</p>

<h3>General opportunities</h3>
<p>All inpatient and outpatient wards including:</p>

<ul class="list--cols">
<li>Cardiac</li>
<li>Day Surgery</li> 
<li>Dermatology</li>
<li>Emergency Department</li>
<li>Gynaecology</li>
<li>Haematology/chemotherapy</li> 
<li>Liver</li>
<li>Medicine</li> 
<li>Neurosciences</li>
<li>Ophthalmology</li>
<li>Radiology and dialysis</li>
<li>Renal</li>
<li>Sexual Health</li>
<li>Stroke</li>
<li>Surgery</li>
</ul>

<h3>Theatre opportunities</h3>

<p>All main theatres and day surgery (scrub, anaesthetics and recovery) including:</p>

<ul class="list--cols">
<li>Anaesthetics and recovery</li>
<li>Cardiac</li>
<li>Cardiac catheter</li>
<li>Endoscopy</li>
<li>Liver transplant</li>
</ul>

<h3>Critical Care opportunities</h3>

<ul class="list--cols">
<li>Coronary care units</li>
<li>Cardiothoracic HDU</li>
<li>Cardiac recovery/HDU</li>
<li>Liver ITU</li>
<li>Medical and Surgical ITU</li> 
<li>Neuro HDU</li>
</ul>

<h3>Childrens&#8217; opportunities</h3>

<p>All childrens&#8217; inpatient and outpatient wards, Paediatric ITU, Neonatal ITU and Childrens&#8217; Emergency Department.</p>

</div><!-- content -->
